             From: andy@petdance.com (Andy Lester)
             Date: Sun, 2 Jul 2006 12:19:08 -0500
             Message-ID: <20060702171908.GA20443@petdance.com>
             
             [ 29276]
             Subject: [PATCH] Makefile.SH: lib/re.pm often messes restarted parallel makes
