             [ 27227]
             SvROK(sv) will never be true when SvIOKp() or SvNOKp() is true, so the
             code inside the if() test in sv_2pv_flags is dead and can be removed.
             
             [ 27235]
             Remove the last (U16) cast for CV depths, missed by change 17835.
             
             [ 27279]
