[ 29794] By: nicholas                              on 2007/01/13  19:26:17
        Log: Integrate:
             [ 26532]
             Subject: [PATCH] Perl_gv_fetchpv vs. gv_fetchpvn
             From: Tels <nospam-abuse@bloodgate.com>
             Date: Thu, 29 Dec 2005 18:32:10 +0100
